pull_request.title: Bump KyleMayes/install-llvm-action from 1.7.0 to 1.8.0
pull_request.body:
Bumps [KyleMayes/install-llvm-action](https://github.com/KyleMayes/install-llvm-action) from 1.7.0 to 1.8.0.
Release notes

Sourced from KyleMayes/install-llvm-action's releases.

v1.8.0

  • Support for LLVM 15.0.7
  • Support for LLVM 16.0.0 (except on macOS because LLVM 16.0.0 was not released for that platform)
Commits
  • 13d5d77 Only trigger actions on master pushes
  • b2f83ab Only test latest LLVM version in action
  • fc7ce6c Add action to test caching support
  • 03ab85b Update referenced version of actions/cache
  • 518e9e6 Add support for LLVM 16.0.0
  • 2be3b80 Add support for LLVM 15.0.7
  • See full diff in compare view
